    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🟥🟥🟥🟧🟧🟧🟨🟨🟨🟩🟩🟩🟦🟦🟦🟪🟪🟪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006970/extras/dd8b6aec72ce41069658fa7ca48bd784.poster.avif?t=1763122224\" width=478 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006970/extras/dd8b6aec72ce41069658fa7ca48bd784.webm?t=1763122224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006970/extras/dd8b6aec72ce41069658fa7ca48bd784.mp4?t=1763122224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Support Pixel Fixel and the developer. Your generous purchase ensures creatives can have an opportunity to build great games like these.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlocking this DLC will grant you the following additional content and rewards in Pixel Fixel: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60 New Levels in the Crazy Shapes game mode!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An entirely new game mode! Gradient Gap; where you have to place the correct color into the correct slot with increasing difficulty.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An entirely new game mode! Spotter; where you have to find the odd one out as fast as you can. It gets more and more difficult the more accurate you are!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Access to a tool for making, and playing with, your own colorways, including in multiplayer sessions! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >12 New colorways! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 New soundscapes (Piano &amp; Fireplace) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 New themes (Beaches &amp; Mountains) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 New secret codes in the collection screen (Check Levels 38, 76, 114, 152, 190!) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Higher limit for custom games and multiplayer games, up to 30x30! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twice as many hints! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorative flair for your username during multiplayer sessions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Last but not least, you'll be supporting a game you love, and a developer who loved making it! </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006970/extras/bb3d1608a357d5efc3f303a8c82a08d5.poster.avif?t=1763122224\" width=478 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006970/extras/bb3d1608a357d5efc3f303a8c82a08d5.webm?t=1763122224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006970/extras/bb3d1608a357d5efc3f303a8c82a08d5.mp4?t=1763122224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🟥🟥🟥🟧🟧🟧🟨🟨🟨🟩🟩🟩🟦🟦🟦🟪🟪🟪</p>",
